        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Kresby Slovenov"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nObrázkov, ktoré zobrazujú našich predkov Slovanov v období včasného stredoveku je ako šafránu, takže poteší každý nový pokus o ich zobrazenie. O to viac poteší, keď &nbsp;kresby sú aj umelecky kvalitné. A to je prípad nielen predchádzajúcej scény víťazstva od Tomáša, ale aj nášho spolupracovníka E. M., ktorý &nbsp;pre nás nakreslil týchto Slovenov a v blízkej budúcnosti sa môžeme tešiť na ďalšie jeho skvelé kresby. Vďaka.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjhe14t42uc5NfCCFxxxtrP7gQSQIHSk1CIDCcIAR6ljGgmbcFvzJoG9SqSKfZxys8oVidrkJ3a_n5vZQU-olCvGA0j4tkalwLaqaAr64_mAqnUShOiB6841jDr1AMnNLIS59lMng4Ump0/s1600/935618_10151549396917347_2062355923_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjhe14t42uc5NfCCFxxxtrP7gQSQIHSk1CIDCcIAR6ljGgmbcFvzJoG9SqSKfZxys8oVidrkJ3a_n5vZQU-olCvGA0j4tkalwLaqaAr64_mAqnUShOiB6841jDr1AMnNLIS59lMng4Ump0/s320/935618_10151549396917347_2062355923_n.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjpHZMaCX6KZhrgYivldwowLHdHxTbegzyh_32tMG71wZ1iYoUez2oKJP1zedmWO0zQEEpOjw1psI4juvua_pxIHVBI9OrRXSJpu9LBJPCx256P6TPoJcBXWRjWGrNmFSatrGZxUktlS8I/s1600/buzogan.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjpHZMaCX6KZhrgYivldwowLHdHxTbegzyh_32tMG71wZ1iYoUez2oKJP1zedmWO0zQEEpOjw1psI4juvua_pxIHVBI9OrRXSJpu9LBJPCx256P6TPoJcBXWRjWGrNmFSatrGZxUktlS8I/s320/buzogan.jpg\" width=\"183\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5m1Nl0V2mtun8GEG-VB-Gc_fe8eA2IxKpS-b9cTGX_7M28NwCmAY2G12Gbluzn40mfWpaugNr0_ykXOUmhHNSFFO8x6Ygbt2BRDYnOXEArAGwFGQby05apEQfDxkUCPmuRt7O5az8btA/s1600/21290_10151546404907347_2076329773_n.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj5m1Nl0V2mtun8GEG-VB-Gc_fe8eA2IxKpS-b9cTGX_7M28NwCmAY2G12Gbluzn40mfWpaugNr0_ykXOUmhHNSFFO8x6Ygbt2BRDYnOXEArAGwFGQby05apEQfDxkUCPmuRt7O5az8btA/s320/21290_10151546404907347_2076329773_n.jpg\" width=\"193\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<br /></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjThl1iWXaWSCSbvjAgJy3Oz-7nUX6RsPl35LSmi3Vzp2k2D58deMDZ4_Xvs6PjGQtfegQCiHUC5dIwdqW9AyHftHrr-gI8ltlJBWakb9vHx-USlggvyu0HTuHmCFPZcyZlrscc4UeodhM/s1600/01.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjThl1iWXaWSCSbvjAgJy3Oz-7nUX6RsPl35LSmi3Vzp2k2D58deMDZ4_Xvs6PjGQtfegQCiHUC5dIwdqW9AyHftHrr-gI8ltlJBWakb9vHx-USlggvyu0HTuHmCFPZcyZlrscc4UeodhM/s320/01.jpg\" width=\"198\" /></a></div>\n<br /></div>\n<div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhB5Jy-8afnmOkBHe4bxqM-aF0UUcUUNr96bCCKvGneb1-fhDj0ybghEX7zqq-Iz4ICqgVJPBn7XjjmIVgKlUyVCurfxIuSOO9ccI_dtEKgM8aPIAQ4Whyphenhyphen2XgJbCaONVg1wVYijFe0PdLA/s1600/Hlavi%25C4%258Dka+web-str%25C3%25A1nky_2.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"95\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhB5Jy-8afnmOkBHe4bxqM-aF0UUcUUNr96bCCKvGneb1-fhDj0ybghEX7zqq-Iz4ICqgVJPBn7XjjmIVgK